name: Amazon CloudFront
description:
http://aws.amazon.com/cloudfront/
Note: cloudfront operates in multiple regions, but these are edge locations and don't map into ”regions” themselves.

name: AWS OpsWorks
description:
http://aws.amazon.com/opsworks/
Note: Although opsworks can launch into any region, the service itself runs out of a particular region.

name: Amazon Route 53
description:
http://aws.amazon.com/route53/
Note: Technically route53 operates in multiple regions, but these are edge locations and don't map into ”regions” themselves.
